title: Pompeo: there’s life after McDreamy
text:
Grey’s Anatomy launches its twelfth season without Patrick Dempsey By Colin Vickery National TV Writer News Corp Australia Network Grey’s Anatomy launches its twelfth season without Patrick Dempsey By Colin Vickery National TV Writer News Corp Australia Network Grey's Anatomy Season 12 promo 0:36 
Grey's Anatomy Season 12 Promo a preview video for Grey's Anatomy Sledgehammer in the United States. October 13th 2015 10 hours ago /video/video.news.com.au/Entertainment/ 
CAN Grey’s Anatomy survive without McDreamy? That is the question fans were asking after Patrick Dempsey, who played Dr Derek Shepherd, left the US medical drama last season. 
Star Ellen Pompeo , who has played Dr Meredith Grey for more than a decade, reckons the answer is a resounding ‘yes’.
